            "title": "A股收升   滬深半日升約0.3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市半日上升，兩市上午成交合計10150.16億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證指數半日收市報3528點，升12點或0.34%，上午高開高走，最多升17點或0.5%，高見3534點，成交4121.29億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指半日收市報10905點，升32點或0.3%，最多升72點或0.67%，高見10946點，成交6028.87億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數收報4053點，升18點或0.47%；創業板指數收報2275點，升5點或0.26%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15100514-a%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%87-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%8d%87%e7%b4%840-3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-ap_China-2.jpg.webp",
